A fold can be executed by placing the cursor in a fold then pressing <shift><enter>.
The Reduce console can be accessed by selecting Plugins->Console->Console and then 
the MPReduce console.




%reduce,title=""
OFF ECHO$

3^1000;

END$
%/reduce





%reduce,title=""
OFF ECHO$

(X+Y+Z)^2;

END$
%/reduce






%reduce,title="Long running calculation."
OFF ECHO$

(X-Y)^100;

END$
%/reduce






